&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Make real decisions around prompt design, model selection, latency/cost/quality tradeoffs, and failure modes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with product, design, and ML teams to build systems that are technically sound &lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt; product-aware&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
