&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We care more about &lt;strong&gt;judgment and ownership&lt;/strong&gt; than credentials.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You’re likely a strong fit if you:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
