&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Narvar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; is hiring! We are hiring a Senior Business Development Representative to help explode our business! As the first line of communication with prospects, ideal BDRs have an understanding of the sales process, excelling at researching leads, starting new relationships, and setting our sales closers up for success. You should be a quick learner with strong communication skills and have the ability to showcase our offerings in a compelling way. Every potential customer is an opportunity for you to boost top-line revenue growth!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
